      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i checked the shims and they seem fine. i also checked the wear sensor but it doesnt look like it's tripped. the noise is really consistent though, almost sounds like metal scraping on metal. could it be a stuck caliper piston? i dont wanna take the whole thing apart unless i have to.",
