      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i tried that and the caliper seems to be moving but i noticed it's not retracting quite as fast as it should. it just feels like something is making this weird, sudden screeching sound right when i engage them. it's such a sharp, piercing noise... kinda sounds almost like a scream. u think it could be something internal in the caliper assembly itself then?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
